# Parser Adapter Rules

Implement `CatalogCollectorPort.collect() -> CollectionResult`.

- Return domain `Product` entities
- Never raise from `collect()` on HTTP errors — set `degraded=True`
- `MockCatalogCollector` when `MOCK_PARSER=true` (wired in Container)

Legacy names: `OzonParser`, `MockParser` are shims in `parser/`.
